    "id": "_953853_1",
    "title": "Research paper topics and instructions",
    "body": "<p>Hi all</p><p>The research paper topics have been uploaded to the Assessment area.&nbsp;&nbsp;Copy attached.</p><p>Thanks for a great couple of days.&nbsp;&nbsp;See you in April.</p><p>Ben</p><br><p><a href=\"https://learn.uq.edu.au/bbcswebdav/internal/courses/LAWS5206_7620_20059/announcements/_953853_1/2026%20Research%20paper%20assessment%20-%20final.pdf?Kq3cZcYS15=72501d55390d4d7f84a9c34f302e8821&VxJw3wfC56=1772365134&3cCnGYSz89=5iG4%2Bh4vr6jpnSnwD7CxW%2BTv23WqiC%2BsIM2UewCAabs%3D\" data-bbtype=\"attachment\" data-bbfile=\"{&quot;alternativeText&quot;:&quot;2026 Research paper assessment - final.pdf&quot;,&quot;displayName&quot;:&quot;2026 Research paper assessment - final.pdf&quot;,&quot;fileName&quot;:&quot;2026 Research paper assessment - final.pdf&quot;,&quot;fileSize&quot;:301514,&quot;mimeType&quot;:&quot;application/pdf&quot;,&quot;render&quot;:&quot;attachment&quot;,&quot;resourceUrl&quot;:&quot;https://learn.uq.edu.au/bbcswebdav/internal/courses/LAWS5206_7620_20059/announcements/_953853_1/2026%20Research%20paper%20assessment%20-%20final.pdf?Kq3cZcYS15=72501d55390d4d7f84a9c34f302e8821&VxJw3wfC56=1772365134&3cCnGYSz89=5iG4%2Bh4vr6jpnSnwD7CxW%2BTv23WqiC%2BsIM2UewCAabs%3D&quot;,&quot;linkName&quot;:&quot;2026 Research paper assessment - final.pdf&quot;}\">2026 Research paper assessment - final.pdf</a></p><br>",
