    "id": "_953768_1",
    "title": "Powerpoint slides from Day 1 (Saturday, 28 Feb)",
    "body": "<p>Hi everyone</p><p>Thanks for a terrific first day today.&nbsp;&nbsp;It is so great to teach a group that's really engaged with the topic &amp; willing to contribute and ask questions.&nbsp;&nbsp;Attached are the Powerpoint slides from today as well as the flyer for the John Emmerson essay competition.</p><p>Also, <a href=\"https://youtu.be/a-1_9-z9rbY?si=hiP9e8U87t_MaoSh\">here is the link</a> to Vanilla Ice explaining the difference between the base lines in Under Pressure vs Ice Ice Baby.</p><p><a href=\"https://learn.uq.edu.au/bbcswebdav/internal/courses/LAWS5206_7620_20059/announcements/_953768_1/2026%20Session%203%20v2%20LAWS5206.pptx?Kq3cZcYS15=72501d55390d4d7f84a9c34f302e8821&VxJw3wfC56=1772365134&3cCnGYSz89=SUj%2FZz4v3htzVZunQFL5T8nyER6uM%2Bwj%2Fj26xcaPAhc%3D\" data-bbtype=\"attachment\" data-bbfile=\"{&quot;alternativeText&quot;:&quot;2026 Session 3 v2 LAWS5206.pptx&quot;,&quot;linkName&quot;:&quot;2026 Session 3 v2 LAWS5206.pptx&quot;,&quot;mimeType&quot;:&quot;application/vnd.openxmlformats-officedocument.presentationml.presentation&quot;,&quot;render&quot;:&quot;attachment&quot;,&quot;fileSize&quot;:13633681,&quot;resourceUrl&quot;:&quot;https://learn.uq.edu.au/bbcswebdav/internal/courses/LAWS5206_7620_20059/announcements/_953768_1/2026%20Session%203%20v2%20LAWS5206.pptx?Kq3cZcYS15=72501d55390d4d7f84a9c34f302e8821&VxJw3wfC56=1772365134&3cCnGYSz89=SUj%2FZz4v3htzVZunQFL5T8nyER6uM%2Bwj%2Fj26xcaPAhc%3D&quot;}\">2026 Session 3 v2 LAWS5206.pptx</a></p><p><a href=\"https://learn.uq.edu.au/bbcswebdav/internal/courses/LAWS5206_7620_20059/announcements/_953768_1/2026%20Session%201%20v2%20-%20LAWS5206%20Copyright%20Law%20.pptx?Kq3cZcYS15=72501d55390d4d7f84a9c34f302e8821&VxJw3wfC56=1772365134&3cCnGYSz89=BbksiZfnKueZQdqt%2B3u8sFSi82NkCsjJKiuYf8JXFXo%3D\" data-bbtype=\"attachment\" data-bbfile=\"{&quot;alternativeText&quot;:&quot;2026 Session 1 v2 - LAWS5206 Copyright Law .pptx&quot;,&quot;linkName&quot;:&quot;2026 Session 1 v2 - LAWS5206 Copyright Law