    "id": "_953298_1",
    "title": "Copyright & Music",
    "body": "<p>On Saturday afternoon, there will be a discussion session on Copyright &amp; Music.</p><br><p>Among other things, we will discuss Federal Court cases involving Men at Work's song <em>Down Under, </em>John Paul Young's <em>Love is in the Air</em> and Twisted Sister's <em>We're Not Gonna Take It.&nbsp;&nbsp;</em>If you're not familiar with those songs, have a listen to them before class.&nbsp;&nbsp;You can find the cases in <a href=\"https://airtable.com/appGVb2VmBZPjod0P/shrdPwDgYSl1CwCMS\">this (short!) reading list</a>.</p>",
    "draft": false,
    "availability": {
      "duration": {
        "type": "Permanent",
