  {
    "id": "_950687_1",
    "title": "Reading material for the first weekend",
    "body": "<p>Hi everyone</p><br><p>There are two lists of recommended reading material for the first weekend <span style=\"text-decoration:underline;\">so far</span> - see below.&nbsp;&nbsp;</p><br><p>Don't panic but there will be more!</p><br><p>Recommended reading for <strong>Session 1</strong> (Introduction and Crash Course in Copyright Law) is <a href=\"https://airtable.com/appGVb2VmBZPjod0P/shrDPcddxTK0KD6ne\">here</a></p><p>Recommended reading for <strong>Sessions 2 and 3 </strong>(Subsistence) is <a href=\"https://airtable.com/appGVb2VmBZPjod0P/shryUZ5reNLUrWLT6\">here</a></p><br><p>You will see that while the reading lists are pretty long (especially the Subsistence one), the required and recommended readings are quite short.&nbsp;&nbsp;Feel free to pick and choose what you read of the \"If interested\" ones.</p><br><p>In addition to these sessions, on the first day we will have a discussion topic called \"Copyright and Music\" which should be fun.&nbsp;&nbsp;</p><br><p>This subject also has it's own Spotify playlist which you can find <a href=\"https://open.spotify.com/playlist/3c3AEz3i5lEJcN1dpok7Sf?si=feBqN-ZnTF6ymxLhc3PTig&amp;pi=YQZfqYKkR5q8c\">here</a>.&nbsp;&nbsp;There's also a guide to the playlist which is attached.&nbsp;&nbsp;You don't need to read the guide or listen to all of the songs before the first weekend (or at all) but it would probably be useful if you have listened to some of them.</p><br><p>If you have any questions at any time, please email me at gardiner@qldbar.asn.au and put LAWS5206 in the subject line</p><br><p>Thanks</p><br><p>Ben</p><p><a href=\"https://learn.uq.edu.au/bbcswebdav/internal/courses/LAWS5206_7620_20059/announcements/_950687_1/Guide%20to%20the%20LAWS5206%20Spotify%20Playlist%20v4.pdf?Kq3cZcYS15=72501d55390d4d7f84a9c34f302e8821&VxJw3wfC56=1772365134&3cCnGYSz89=JxP61jb62cIEVO9ckmN0K8neQOJG47BgNuxjYPQs8Bg%3D\" data-bbtype=\"attachment\" data-bbfile=\"{&quot;alternativeText&quot;:&quot;Guide to the LAWS5206 Spotify Playlist v4.pdf&quot;,&quot;displayName&quot;:&quot;Guide to the LAWS5206 Spotify Playlist v4.pdf&quot;,&quot;fileName&quot;:&quot;Guide to the LAWS5206 Spotify Playlist v4.pdf&quot;,&quot;fileSize&quot;:309730,&quot;mimeType&quot;:&quot;application/pdf&quot;,&quot;render&quot;:&quot;attachment&quot;,&quot;resourceUrl&quot;:&quot;https://learn.uq.edu.au/bbcswebdav/internal/courses/LAWS5206_7620_20059/announcements/_950687_1/Guide%20to%20the%20LAWS5206%20Spotify%20Playlist%20v4.pdf?Kq3cZcYS15=72501d55390d4d7f84a9c34f302e8821&VxJw3wfC56=1772365134&3cCnGYSz89=JxP61jb62cIEVO9ckmN0K8neQOJG47BgNuxjYPQs8Bg%3D&quot;,&quot;linkName&quot;:&quot;Guide to the LAWS5206 Spotify Playlist v4.pdf&quot;}\">Guide to the LAWS5206 Spotify Playlist v4.pdf</a></p><br>",
